   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <strong>
   You are the steward of these lands
  </strong>
  and can help your kin succeed through digging, encouragement, and more. Assist your kin in their cause by clicking, swiping, and hovering your cursor to expedite their mission in recovering the lost essence.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="160" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505770/extras/4ba335cca68fadb935ef3fed0142c9fb.poster.avif?t=1768579073" width="616">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505770/extras/4ba335cca68fadb935ef3fed0142c9fb.webm?t=1768579073" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
